{"tid":2128052,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[豁免檢疫] 本港出現首宗中港車司機確診","createTime":"2020-07-27T16:31:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T01:06:58.000Z","uid":73883,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0f7120de48ddcaf64ad3ca8f64ded65afa31ac94","tid":2128052,"uid":73883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T16:31:08.000Z","msg":"62歲中港車司機確診　成跨境車司機首例<br />\n<br />\n［Now新聞台］本港出現首宗中港車司機確診，患者上周曾到龍崗，廣東省將加強中港跨境貨車司機入境管制。<br />\n<br />\n本港新增的新冠病毒確診個案中，包括一名62歲中港車司機，是本地跨境車司機確診首例。衞生防護中心指，司機住上水彩園邨彩華樓。<br />\n<br />\n深圳衞健委表示，這名司機7月18日晚上，從文錦渡入境內地，當時核酸檢測呈陰性，他之後在龍崗一間印刷廠及一家腸粉店逗留過，直至上周三，經文錦渡回港，周日確診。<br />\n<br />\n與確診貨車司機同公司及有接觸的司機，14天內亦不應駕車進入內地。<br />\n<br />\n另外，廣東省加強中港跨境貨車司機入境管制，跨境貨車司機在香港居住的樓宇過往14天內，曾有新冠病毒確診個案，他們入境豁免隔離的資格會被暫時取消，期間內地口岸單位不會為司機進行核酸檢測，受影響的司機須於第15天或以後，才可到口岸進行核酸檢測採樣。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=399549\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D399549&d=oFI5KSBgBGvHra6dYUznBgEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=c060d124\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D399549&h=2bb2ce19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=399549</a>"},{"pid":"276d2879bf0f956f3b85225eaaffee488581169c","tid":2128052,"uid":73883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T16:34:59.000Z","msg":"Molamola <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FtOAK7S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFtOAK7S.png&h=49875d54&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a758d696bcc94437be2dd771beb45746f6aaf621","tid":2128052,"uid":127929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T16:36:05.000Z","msg":"其實中國係<span class=\"red\">好撚嚴重</span>, 只係佢地唔報<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07d998ce898332fe675a3